			<font class="lt4"><i>Immunostaining of dendritic cells in the tick feeding site of  [e]lt;/i[e]rt;rhipicephalus microplus[e]lt;i[e]rt; (acari:ixodidae) in f2 holstein x gir crossbred cattle artificially infested</i></font>
